text: Joe Biden is at the Grand Canyon today as he makes a desperate attempt to sell the so-called “Inflation Reduction Act” — also known as the Bidenflation Scam — to Americans, almost a year after its passage. One year later, there’s a reason just 39 percent of Americans say they support the Bidenflation Scam: • It does nothing to solve inflation.
